### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api
@token = your-jwt-token-here
@templateId = template-uuid-here

### ============================================
### TEMPLATES ENDPOINTS
### ============================================

### Get all templates
GET {{baseUrl}}/templates
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get template by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/templates/{{templateId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


